N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 113.12 - Names of parties or counsel endorsed on all papers

State Regulations

All appeal papers must be endorsed with the name, post
office address and telephone number of the party submitting the same or if a
party is represented by counsel, with the name, post office address and
telephone number of his counsel. Notes
